---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="High-Net-Worth Divorce in Maryland | Complex Asset Division Attorneys | Child Custody with a Plan"
  description="Maryland high-net-worth divorce attorneys handling complex portfolios, retirement accounts, real estate, investments, and business interests. Strategic. Discreet. Proven. Call (301) 289-8917."
  ogTitle="High-Net-Worth Divorce Maryland | Child Custody with a Plan"
  ogDescription="When the stakes are highest, experience matters. Maryland attorneys for high-asset divorce involving investment portfolios, retirement accounts, real estate, and business interests."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#0D6E6E] text-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] bg-repeat"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-[#D4A843] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">Complex Asset Divorce</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-5">
        High-Net-Worth Divorce<br class="hidden md:block" /> in Maryland
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        When your marital estate includes millions in assets — investment portfolios, retirement accounts, multiple properties, business interests, and more — you need attorneys who have successfully handled cases of this magnitude.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/free-consultation" class="bg-[#D4A843] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b8902f] transition-colors">
          Book Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:3012898917" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-[#0D6E6E] transition-colors">
          (301) 289-8917
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-3">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#0D6E6E]">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <a href="/divorce" class="hover:text-[#0D6E6E]">Divorce</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">High-Net-Worth Divorce</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Proven Experience -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">Proven High-Asset Experience</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            High-net-worth divorces are categorically different from routine family law matters. The sheer complexity of identifying, valuing, and distributing a large marital estate — with all its competing interests and tax implications — demands attorneys who have navigated these waters before.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Our attorneys have successfully tried contested high-asset divorce cases exceeding $2 million in total marital assets. We coordinate a team of financial experts, forensic accountants, and business valuators to build airtight cases for our clients.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Whether you are seeking to protect what you've built or ensure you receive your fair share of a complex marital estate, our attorneys in Rockville and Baltimore are ready to guide you with precision and strategic insight.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-[#D4A843]/10 border border-[#D4A843]/30 rounded-xl p-5">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0D6E6E] mb-1">$2M+</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">High-asset contested cases successfully tried by our attorneys</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0D6E6E]/5 border border-[#0D6E6E]/20 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Asset Types We Handle</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
              {[
                "Investment and brokerage portfolios",
                "401(k), 403(b), pension, and IRA accounts",
                "Executive compensation: RSUs, stock options, deferred comp",
                "Commercial and residential real estate",
                "Business interests and professional practices",
                "Private equity and venture capital holdings",
                "Trust and estate interests",
                "Art, jewelry, collectibles, and luxury assets",
                "Cryptocurrency and digital assets",
                "Offshore accounts and foreign assets"
              ].map(asset => (
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#D4A843]">•</span>
                  {asset}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Issues -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-3">Key Issues in High-Net-Worth Divorce</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Every high-net-worth divorce involves a unique constellation of legal and financial challenges. Here's how we address the most common ones.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            title: "Retirement Account Division & QDROs",
            icon: "🏦",
            desc: "Dividing 401(k)s, pensions, and other qualified retirement plans requires a Qualified Domestic Relations Order (QDRO). Errors in QDRO drafting can cost you years of benefits. We work with QDRO specialists to ensure accurate, enforceable orders that protect your retirement security."
          },
          {
            title: "Real Estate & Multiple Properties",
            icon: "🏠",
            desc: "From the marital home to vacation properties, rental portfolios, and commercial real estate — each property requires individual valuation, mortgage analysis, and strategic planning. We address equity distribution, buyout options, sale proceeds, and rental income streams."
          },
          {
            title: "Investment Portfolios & Brokerage Accounts",
            icon: "📈",
            desc: "Dividing investments isn't as simple as splitting the balance — tax basis, unrealized gains, and timing of transfers all matter enormously. We analyze the after-tax value of every asset to negotiate outcomes that are truly equitable, not just equal on paper."
          },
          {
            title: "Executive Compensation Packages",
            icon: "💼",
            desc: "Unvested stock options, RSUs, deferred bonuses, and performance shares require careful classification. Which were earned during the marriage? How are unvested awards treated under Maryland law? We know how to argue for the most favorable characterization."
          },
          {
            title: "Business & Professional Practice Interests",
            icon: "🏢",
            desc: "Business valuation is one of the most contested issues in high-net-worth divorce. We work with certified business valuators and counter biased valuations from opposing experts. We protect operational control while ensuring fair treatment of all business-related assets."
          },
          {
            title: "Hidden Assets & Financial Discovery",
            icon: "🔍",
            desc: "High-asset spouses sometimes attempt to hide, undervalue, or transfer assets before or during divorce. We employ aggressive discovery — subpoenas, depositions, forensic accounting — to ensure full financial disclosure and prevent fraudulent dissipation."
          }
        ].map(issue => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="text-3xl flex-shrink-0">{issue.icon}</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{issue.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{issue.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Expert Team -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#0D6E6E]">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">A Full Expert Team Behind Your Case</h2>
      <p class="text-white/75 text-center mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">High-net-worth divorce requires more than great attorneys — it requires a coordinated team of financial professionals. We build that team for you.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          { expert: "Forensic Accountants", role: "Trace assets, identify hidden funds, analyze business records, and challenge opposing financial data." },
          { expert: "Business Valuators", role: "Certified valuators using NACVA and AICPA standards to produce defensible business value opinions." },
          { expert: "Real Estate Appraisers", role: "Independent appraisals of residential and commercial properties to establish accurate fair market value." },
          { expert: "QDRO Specialists", role: "Specialists who draft Qualified Domestic Relations Orders for every type of retirement account." },
          { expert: "Financial Advisors", role: "Help you understand the long-term financial impact of settlement decisions before you commit." },
          { expert: "Tax Professionals", role: "Address capital gains, transfer tax, and income tax implications of every element of the settlement." }
        ].map(e => (
          <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-5 text-white">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#D4A843] mb-2">{e.expert}</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">{e.role}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Spousal Support in HNW -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-5">Spousal Support in High-Net-Worth Cases</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Alimony takes on extraordinary significance in high-net-worth divorce. The difference between a favorable and unfavorable spousal support order can mean hundreds of thousands of dollars over time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Maryland courts have significant discretion in setting alimony. Factors like the standard of living during marriage, each spouse's earning capacity, length of marriage, and financial needs all influence the amount and duration.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We fight to ensure any alimony order — whether you're paying or receiving — accurately reflects the financial reality of the marriage and the legitimate needs of both parties going forward.
          </p>
          <a href="/spousal-support" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#0D6E6E] font-semibold mt-5 hover:underline">
            Learn More About Spousal Support <span>→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">If You're the Higher Earner</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              {[
                "Challenge permanent alimony requests with evidence of earning capacity",
                "Argue for rehabilitative alimony with defined end date",
                "Address lifestyle inflation during marriage vs. actual need",
                "Include automatic modification provisions for changed circumstances",
                "Ensure alimony terminates upon remarriage or cohabitation"
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#D4A843]">✓</span>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">If You're the Lower Earner</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              {[
                "Document the marital standard of living comprehensively",
                "Quantify your non-monetary contributions to the marriage",
                "Establish appropriate support level to maintain lifestyle",
                "Seek indefinite alimony where circumstances justify",
                "Protect against premature modification attempts"
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-[#D4A843]">✓</span>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-3">Our High-Net-Worth Divorce Process</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We combine our proprietary PROMISE Framework with specialized high-asset expertise to deliver results that protect your wealth.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        {[
          { phase: "01", title: "Comprehensive Assessment", desc: "Deep-dive review of all financial records, asset schedules, business interests, and retirement accounts to map the full marital estate." },
          { phase: "02", title: "Expert Team Assembly", desc: "We identify and engage the right financial experts for your specific asset mix — valuators, forensic accountants, appraisers, QDRO specialists." },
          { phase: "03", title: "Strategic Positioning", desc: "Develop a clear theory of the case that positions your interests favorably — in negotiation, mediation, or trial." },
          { phase: "04", title: "Resolution & Enforcement", desc: "Achieve the best possible outcome and ensure every provision of your settlement is airtight and enforceable." }
        ].map(p => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#D4A843] mb-3">{p.phase}</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{p.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">When the Stakes Are Highest</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Your financial future depends on the quality of representation you receive today. Book a confidential consultation with our Maryland high-net-worth divorce attorneys.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/free-consultation" class="bg-[#0D6E6E] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#0a5a5a] transition-colors">
          Book Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:3012898917" class="bg-[#D4A843] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#b8902f] transition-colors">
          Call (301) 289-8917
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">Rockville: 100 Park Ave Suite 205 · Baltimore: 1537 Light St #100 · Mon–Fri 9AM–9PM</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
